video.title: Booba
video.synopsis: The world is a mystery to little Booba. But he approaches the curiosities around him with wonder, finding adventure in his everyday surroundings.

episodes.synopsis: Booba goes on a candy hunt inside a house decorated for Halloween.
episodes.title: Halloween

episodes.synopsis: Booba desperately wants to learn how to fly, so Mr. Beak tries to help.
episodes.title: Flying

episodes.synopsis: Booba attempts to get to his favorite food — cheese — inside a refrigerator, but not if Noodle can help it!
episodes.title: Kitchen Adventures

episodes.synopsis: A Christmas display at the mall and a helpful snowman put Booba in a festive mood.
episodes.title: Santa’s Grotto

episodes.synopsis: Sticky notes, a photocopier and more are all fair game when Booba explores an empty office.
episodes.title: Office

episodes.synopsis: Booba tries to put on a makeshift show in the circus ring, but Spike doesn't seem interested.
episodes.title: Circus Adventure

episodes.synopsis: Booba prepares to visit the beach through a magic wardrobe but gets transported to a futuristic world instead.
episodes.title: Booba in the Future

episodes.synopsis: A hot and thirsty Booba faces a challenge when he tries to juice some fresh fruit.
episodes.title: Juice

episodes.synopsis: Booba and Loola have fun in an art studio and get creative with modeling clay.
episodes.title: Clay crafts

episodes.synopsis: Booba enjoys a visit to the firefighting museum but must pull off a rescue of his own when Mr. Beak gets into a jam.
episodes.title: Firefighter

episodes.synopsis: Booba makes mischief at a chocolate factory while Loola tries to do her job decorating Easter eggs.
episodes.title: Easter

episodes.synopsis: After losing a tooth, Booba has high hopes for a visit from the tooth fairy.
episodes.title: Tooth Fairy

episodes.synopsis: Booba and his friends try different methods as they try to open a fresh watermelon to share.
episodes.title: Watermelon

episodes.synopsis: Booba tries his luck at several games at an amusement park in an attempt to win a teddy bear prize.
episodes.title: Funfair

episodes.synopsis: A genie tries to take a break but Booba and his friends have so many wishes they'd like to get granted first!
episodes.title: Magic Lamp

episodes.synopsis: Booba and his teddy bear explore a science museum, where an experiment brings to life a ball of cheese that Booba tries to eat.
episodes.title: Science Museum

episodes.synopsis: The magic wardrobe transports Booba to the Wild West, where he must try to retrieve a stolen wheel of cheese.
episodes.title: Wild West

episodes.synopsis: Booba travels underwater in a submarine and meets a playful fish, then tries to snap up a shiny pearl from an oyster.
episodes.title: Submarine Adventure

episodes.synopsis: When Booba has no one to play with, he uses a magic photo booth to create clones of himself with different personalities.
episodes.title: Magic Photo Booth

episodes.synopsis: Booba dives into a ball pit and gets transported to an underwater domain, where he befriends the Sea King.
episodes.title: Underwater Adventure

episodes.synopsis: Booba uses a whisk, chopsticks and even a tennis racket to try and open an unlabeled tin can to find out what's inside.
episodes.title: Tin Trouble

episodes.synopsis: The magic wardrobe sends Booba in his rocket ship to another planet, where he makes a new alien friend.
episodes.title: Space Adventure

episodes.synopsis: Booba, Mr. Beak and Loola tackle a tricky obstacle course to reach the sweet prize at the finish line.
episodes.title: Obstacle Course Chaos

episodes.synopsis: Booba attempts to assemble a toy robot but may have gotten the instructions wrong along the way!
episodes.title: The Robot

episodes.synopsis: Booba has trouble keeping quiet in the library, especially after finding a book with a mischievous genie inside.
episodes.title: Library

episodes.synopsis: Loola the witch gives Booba lessons on how to properly ride a flying broomstick.
episodes.title: Magic Broomstick

episodes.synopsis: Booba and Loola try to run away from a colorful egg until it hatches with a special surprise inside.
episodes.title: Toy Store

episodes.synopsis: When balls start flying in all directions at a miniature golf course, Booba and Loola go on a wacky adventure to retrieve them.
episodes.title: Crazy Golf

episodes.synopsis: Determined to win a trophy, Booba practices his skills at the bowling alley until a spiky friend interrupts his game.
episodes.title: Bowling

episodes.synopsis: Loola hits the stage to dance ballet as a hungry Booba joins the performance.
episodes.title: Ballet

episodes.synopsis: From a jack-in-the-box to a jar of candy, Booba's trip to the store is filled with fun distractions — and a pesky parrot.
episodes.title: Gift Shop

episodes.synopsis: On a spaceship, Booba has a blast defying gravity with his teddy bear companion.
episodes.title: Spaceship

episodes.synopsis: Surrounded by instruments, Booba and his buddies cause musical chaos before making a sweet melody.
episodes.title: Music Shop

episodes.synopsis: Booba swipes Loola's magical chalk, which brings every drawing to life.
episodes.title: Magic chalk

episodes.synopsis: Booba and Loola's imaginations run wild during playtime in the attic.
episodes.title: Treasure Map

episodes.synopsis: During a trip to the past, Booba meets a prehistoric pal. Together, they try to shake down a palm tree for bananas.
episodes.title: Magic Wardrobe

episodes.synopsis: When a blast from the past comes to visit Booba, their cravings lead them on a mission to pack snacks.
episodes.title: Guest

episodes.synopsis: On the set of his own show, Booba, along with Loola and Googa, show off their moves for a dance performance.
episodes.title: Show

episodes.synopsis: With a brand-new remote in his hands, Booba has full control of a high-tech house. Fun for him, but very annoying for his rat friend!
episodes.title: Remote Control

episodes.synopsis: After reading a comic book, Booba's inspired to become a caped crusader himself! He's got the outfit. Now, he just needs the superpowers.
episodes.title: Super Booba

episodes.synopsis: Watch out -- Booba's in an empty ice hockey rink! He has no idea how to play, but that doesn't stop him from trying.
episodes.title: Hockey

episodes.synopsis: It's the holidays and there's a gorgeous tree -- without decorations. To set things right, Booba and his friends are going to need a Christmas miracle.
episodes.title: Christmas Tree

episodes.synopsis: A little critter has stolen Booba's lollipop. To get it back, he'll have to chase the thief all over the fun-filled playground!
episodes.title: Playtime

episodes.synopsis: One second, Booba's enjoying ice cream while playing a computer game. The next, he's stuck inside a computer game himself! Will he taste victory?
episodes.title: Video Game

episodes.synopsis: Is that a ghost or someone messing around with a sheet? Either way, Booba's terrified!
episodes.title: Ghost

episodes.synopsis: It's sandwich-making time! Booba doesn't know which is more fun: making delicious food or eating it.
episodes.title: Sandwiches

episodes.synopsis: As soon as he enters the kitchen, Booba is fascinated by the big, cool box full of food. He really wants the wheel of cheese, but he can't reach it!
episodes.title: Kitchen

episodes.synopsis: Things are strange and dangerous in this room. There's a big, slippery tub that Booba gets trapped in and lots of loud appliances that scare him.
episodes.title: Bathroom

episodes.synopsis: There are so many colorful, fun things to play with in this room! There's a ball pit for Booba to dive into and toy soldiers for him to battle.
episodes.title: Nursery

episodes.synopsis: This room looks very serious to Booba. There are desks and glasses and a computer that makes weird sounds -- and even a thing that punches holes!
episodes.title: Office

episodes.synopsis: Booba immediately topples a house of cards, loses control of a unicycle and then swallows a bunch of billiard balls. What kind of a room is this?
episodes.title: Game Room

episodes.synopsis: Rows of desks, a blackboard, a microscope -- this must be a classroom!  Booba discovers how risky laser pointers can be.
episodes.title: Biology Cabinet

episodes.synopsis: Booba is determined to blow out the holiday candle but it's really, really hard. Maybe he needs a fire extinguisher.
episodes.title: The Candle

episodes.synopsis: There's a shiny, red car in this garage that Booba can't resist exploring. What could go wrong?
episodes.title: Garage

episodes.synopsis: It's nighttime and Booba has made his way to the attic. From wind-up toys to snow globes, this room is full of such random little things.
episodes.title: Attic

episodes.synopsis: While walking past shop windows, Booba spots a beautiful red bowtie that he's determined to get his hands on.
episodes.title: Bow Tie

episodes.synopsis: While in a sunny country home, Booba discovers a delicious-looking chunk of cheese -- but it's stuck in a weird device.
episodes.title: Mouse Trap

episodes.synopsis: After getting trapped in a suitcase at the airport, Booba finds himself in an artist's apartment and gets inspired to try his hand at painting.
episodes.title: Painting

episodes.synopsis: There are delicious cakes and confectionaries everywhere! This must be Booba's lucky day.
episodes.title: Bakery

episodes.synopsis: Booba walks into an empty circus and discovers a very strange top hat that seems to have a mind of its own.
episodes.title: Circus

episodes.synopsis: Snacks on the table, balloons everywhere -- this must be a party! Booba wants to grab a red balloon, but it's a lot harder than it looks.
episodes.title: Party

episodes.synopsis: Booba finds himself in a big, empty movie theater lobby, where he discovers the gum ball machine and learns how challenging chewing gum can be.
episodes.title: Cinema Hall

episodes.synopsis: At first, this basement is too dark. But when Booba turns on the light, it's way too bright!
episodes.title: Bulb

episodes.synopsis: It's time for Booba to cook! He flips through a recipe book and decides to make a burger -- with a few extra ingredients.
episodes.title: Burger

episodes.synopsis: Booba gets off at a subway station with a giant teddy bear in his hands. He needs to go up the escalator, but the teddy bear is making it very hard!
episodes.title: Metro

episodes.synopsis: There are so many yummy-looking things at the supermarket, but what Booba really wants is that mouth-watering wheel of cheese.
episodes.title: Supermarket

episodes.synopsis: Inside a big, empty concert hall, Booba meets a rat who is pretty clever. They both want the conductor's baton, but the rat gets it first!
episodes.title: Concert Hall

episodes.synopsis: There's a parrot in the kitchen and it keeps stealing Booba's food -- but Booba's got a few tricks up his sleeve!
episodes.title: Grapes

episodes.synopsis: It's boogie time! Booba dances with his friends in a big, empty disco.
episodes.title: Disco

episodes.synopsis: Booba is having a wonderful, cheese-filled dream, but something keeps waking him up. What could it be?
episodes.title: Noise

episodes.synopsis: Feeling thirsty, Booba tries to get some water out of the water cooler at the gym -- but then he accidentally turns the treadmill on!
episodes.title: Fitness Club

episodes.synopsis: While rifling through the attic, Booba has a close encounter with a flying saucer.
episodes.title: UFO

episodes.synopsis: Summer time is here and Booba is ready for some sunbathing. Now if only he could find some sun!
episodes.title: Terrace

episodes.synopsis: Traveling by train, Booba is fascinated by everything around him. His bed, his pillow, the windows -- and the emergency brake!
episodes.title: Train

episodes.synopsis: Booba is traveling by plane, but there's something a little weird. All the passengers are teddy bears, and Booba is the pilot!
episodes.title: Aircraft

episodes.synopsis: There's a big dinosaur in this museum, and it's got Booba's precious banana! He's going to have to do something about that.
episodes.title: Museum

episodes.synopsis: The sun is shining, the grass is green and the apples are ripe for the picking. There's so much for Booba to explore on this farm.
episodes.title: Farm

episodes.synopsis: Booba walks into a house and finds a bright red ball. He really wants to play with it, but it keeps rolling away!
episodes.title: Ball
